有個方法可以試<br />
條片有成1GB 但我3分鐘先load到3MB試唔到<br />
<br />
chrome 打開 <a href="https://cloud189-gz-corp.oos-gz.ctyunapi.cn" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloud189-gz-corp.oos-gz.ctyunapi.cn&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu5ODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=5a7c5841" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://cloud189-gz-corp.oos-gz.ctyunapi.cn</a><br />
F12 -&gt; Consoles<br />
Run:<br />
<pre><code data-type="">
let backup;

fetch(&quot;&lt;links&gt;&quot;)
    .then(res =&gt; res.blob())
    .then(res =&gt; {

         backup = res;

        let a = document.createElement('a');

        a.href = URL.createObjectURL(res);

        a.download = &quot;output.mp4&quot;;

        document.body.appendChild(a);

        a.click();

    });</code></pre>
